
<head>
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Invoicing</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    /* ========= <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Invoicing Page ========= */

    .inv-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-green: #16a34a;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      --radius-lg: 18px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 72px;
    }

    .inv-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .inv-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- Hero ---------- */

    .inv-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .inv-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .inv-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .inv-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .inv-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.2vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .inv-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .inv-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .inv-hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .inv-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .inv-hero-foot {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .inv-hero-foot span {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .inv-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .inv-hero-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .inv-hero-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .inv-hero-chip {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
    }

    .inv-hero-status {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.7);
      color: #bbf7d0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .inv-hero-topline {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .inv-hero-topline span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .inv-hero-topline strong {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .inv-hero-items {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px 10px 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .inv-hero-items-header,
    .inv-hero-items-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2.4fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .inv-hero-items-header {
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .inv-hero-items-row {
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .inv-hero-items-row strong {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .inv-hero-summary {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .inv-hero-summary dl {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .inv-hero-summary dt {
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .inv-hero-summary dd {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .inv-hero-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .inv-hero-meta code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
        "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .inv-hero-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .inv-hero-footer span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .inv-hero-footer-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }

    .inv-hero-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ---------- Intro ---------- */

    .inv-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .inv-intro h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .inv-intro p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .inv-intro strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---------- Top-level feature grid ---------- */

    .inv-feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .inv-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .inv-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .inv-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .inv-feature-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .inv-feature-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .inv-feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .inv-feature-meta {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ---------- Two-column feature sections ---------- */

    .inv-section-block {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }

    .inv-section-block.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .inv-section-block,
      .inv-section-block.reverse {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .inv-section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .inv-section-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .inv-section-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .inv-section-text + .inv-section-text {
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .inv-section-list {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .inv-section-list li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .inv-section-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .inv-section-card h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .inv-section-card p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .inv-pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .inv-pill {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .inv-pill.alt {
      background: #ecfdf5;
      color: #166534;
    }

    /* ---------- Section headings ---------- */

    .inv-section-heading {
      margin: 40px 0 16px;
    }

    .inv-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .inv-section-main-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .inv-section-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    /* ---------- Testimonials ---------- */

    .inv-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0 52px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .inv-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .inv-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .inv-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    }

    .inv-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .inv-testimonial-logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .inv-testimonial-heading {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .inv-testimonial-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .inv-testimonial-person {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .inv-testimonial-person strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- Articles ---------- */

    .inv-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .inv-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .inv-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .inv-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .inv-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .inv-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .inv-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .inv-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .inv-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .inv-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ---------- Newsletter ---------- */

    .inv-newsletter {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #111827, #020617);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .inv-newsletter {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .inv-newsletter h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .inv-newsletter p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .inv-newsletter-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .inv-newsletter-input {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
      min-width: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      outline: none;
    }

    .inv-newsletter-input::placeholder {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .inv-newsletter-btn {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #f9fafb;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .inv-newsletter-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="inv-page" id="invoicing">
  <div class="inv-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="inv-hero">
      <div>
        <h1 class="inv-title">
          Send clear, accurate invoices in <span>seconds, not evenings.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="inv-sub">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> turns your jobs into professional invoices automatically, with the right services,
          prices, taxes and branding every time. Send them by SMS or email, and track who has paid –
          all in one place.
        </p>
        <p class="inv-hero-note">
          No more retyping job details, chasing paper records or wondering what’s been invoiced. <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>
          keeps everything connected and up to date.
        </p>

        <div class="inv-cta-row">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">See pricing</a>
        </div>
        <p class="inv-hero-foot">
          <span>Invoicing, payments and customer records, all in <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: invoicing mockup -->
      <div class="inv-hero-media">
        <div class="inv-hero-card">
          <div class="inv-hero-header">
            <div class="inv-hero-chip"><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> · Invoice #00421</div>
            <div class="inv-hero-status">Sent · Awaiting payment</div>
          </div>

          <div class="inv-hero-topline">
            <span>Customer: <strong>Sarah Collins</strong></span>
            <span>Due: <strong>07 Mar 2025</strong></span>
          </div>

          <div class="inv-hero-items">
            <div class="inv-hero-items-header">
              <span>Description</span>
              <span>Qty</span>
              <span>Amount</span>
            </div>
            <div class="inv-hero-items-row">
              <span><strong>Exterior window clean – Route 3</strong></span>
              <span>1</span>
              <span>$95.00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="inv-hero-items-row">
              <span>Gutter inspection &amp; debris removal</span>
              <span>1</span>
              <span>$55.00</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="inv-hero-summary">
            <dl>
              <dt>Subtotal</dt>
              <dd>$150.00</dd>
            </dl>
            <dl>
              <dt>Tax (10%)</dt>
              <dd>$15.00</dd>
            </dl>
            <dl>
              <dt>Total</dt>
              <dd>$165.00</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="inv-hero-meta">
            Template: <code>Standard invoice · {{customer_name}} · {{job_date}}</code>
          </div>

          <div class="inv-hero-footer">
            <span>
              <span class="inv-hero-footer-dot"></span>
              Created directly from completed job
            </span>
            <span>Send via SMS &amp; email in one click</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inv-hero-shadow"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="inv-intro">
      <h2>Invoicing that fits how you actually work.</h2>
      <p>
        When your schedule is busy, you don’t have time to rebuild invoices from scratch. <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>
        pulls in the jobs you’ve already completed, including services, pricing and taxes, and lets you
        review and send invoices in bulk or one by one.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use branded templates, add custom line items when needed and send invoices by SMS and email with
        links to your payment options or customer portal.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Results: fewer missed invoices, fewer errors and a clearer view of who’s paid and who hasn’t.</strong>
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- TOP-LEVEL FEATURE GRID -->
    <section class="inv-feature-grid">
      <article class="inv-feature-card">
        <p class="inv-feature-label">Job-based Invoicing</p>
        <h3 class="inv-feature-title">Turn completed jobs into invoices in a click</h3>
        <p class="inv-feature-text">
          Select jobs from your schedule and let <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> build invoices using your saved services and
          price lists. Adjust if needed, then send.
        </p>
        <p class="inv-feature-meta">
          Perfect for route-based work and teams completing lots of small jobs each day.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="inv-feature-card">
        <p class="inv-feature-label">Recurring Invoices</p>
        <h3 class="inv-feature-title">Set it once for regular work</h3>
        <p class="inv-feature-text">
          For customers on maintenance plans or subscription-style arrangements, set up recurring invoices
          that are created automatically on your chosen schedule.
        </p>
        <p class="inv-feature-meta">
          Combine with automatic payments for completely hands-off billing.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="inv-feature-card">
        <p class="inv-feature-label">Batch Invoicing</p>
        <h3 class="inv-feature-title">Handle end-of-day invoicing in minutes</h3>
        <p class="inv-feature-text">
          Filter by date, route, staff member or status, then batch-create invoices for all completed jobs.
          Review totals and send everything in one go.
        </p>
        <p class="inv-feature-meta">
          Less time in front of the computer, more time serving customers.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- DEEPER FEATURE SECTIONS -->

    <!-- Job-based invoicing + Templates -->
    <section class="inv-section-block">
      <div>
        <p class="inv-section-label">Job-based Invoicing</p>
        <h2 class="inv-section-title">Start with the work you’ve actually done.</h2>
        <p class="inv-section-text">
          Because invoicing is built on top of your <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> schedule, every completed job already has
          the customer, address, services and agreed prices attached. Turning that into an invoice is a
          natural next step.
        </p>
        <p class="inv-section-text">
